{
  "id": "adv_love_2603_03_01",
  "title": "Episode 3 Part 1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の仕事帰りの夜",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1573.3334208
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "うっそぴょーん",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh012.wav",
              "text": "う、うっそぴょーん\n嫌だなぁ、冗談に決まってるじゃないですか\nあれ？　真に受けちゃいました？",
              "startTime": 183.9539015691,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 192.8205794255
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio014.wav",
              "text": "そうよね、冗談に決まってるわよね\nこんな私を好きになる訳ないのに……\n私ったら真に受けて……",
              "startTime": 192.8205794255,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio015.wav",
              "text": "貴方といると飽きないわね\nでも、そういう冗談ばかり言ってると\nいつか後悔するわよ",
              "startTime": 202.6872460921,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio016.wav",
              "text": "あの時、茶化さずに\nちゃんと告白していたら良かった、って……",
              "startTime": 211.5872460921,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 217.6240715583
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh013.wav",
              "text": "えっ？\nそれって、もしかして……",
              "startTime": 218.3205794255,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 222.1539076725
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh014.wav",
              "text": "莉央さん。今の告白、やり直させて下さい\n今度は冗談で誤魔化したりしません\nちゃんと本心を言いますから",
              "startTime": 222.1539076725,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "本気です。俺は莉央さんが好きです",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh015.wav",
              "text": "もちろん本気です。一人の人間として\n尊敬していますが、それ以上に、一人の\n女性として俺は莉央さんを愛しています！",
              "startTime": 231.9205743391,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "瑠依に頼む",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "――三十分後",
              "startTime": 366.0206163406,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 367.2206427892
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio020.wav",
              "text": "天動さんが私を呼び出すなんて\nめずらしいわね\nそれで、私に聞きたいことって何かしら",
              "startTime": 368.0538730858,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rui006.wav",
              "text": "単刀直入にお尋ねします。莉央さんは\n{user}君のことが\n好きなんですか？",
              "startTime": 376.0538730858,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 377.9539496739
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio021.wav",
              "text": "ど、どうして急にそんなことを……\nそういえば、貴方は彼と仲が良かったわね\nそう……告白のことを聞いたのね？",
              "startTime": 382.1205397525,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 387.4539496739
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio022.wav",
              "text": "実を言うと自分の気持ちがよく分からないの\n彼は悪い人じゃないと思うけど、好きかと\n聞かれると……。貴方は彼をどう思う？",
              "startTime": 395.6205316144,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rui007.wav",
              "text": "彼は優しくて誠実な人です\n思いやりがあって、自分以外の誰かの\nために頑張ることが出来る人です",
              "startTime": 409.4871921776,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio023.wav",
              "text": "そうね……私もそう思うわ\n優しくて誠実で誰かのために頑張れる……\nそういう人だから、私は彼のことを……",
              "startTime": 417.6538446027,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio024.wav",
              "text": "ありがとう、天動さん\n貴方と話したおかげで\n自分の気持ちがはっきりしたわ",
              "startTime": 431.3538344302,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "瑠依に頼まない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 439.4205010968
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh025.wav",
              "text": "ありがとう。でも遠慮しておくよ\nこういうことは人任せにするんじゃなく\n自分が相手と向き合うべきだと思うから",
              "startTime": 439.4205010968,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rui008.wav",
              "text": "そうね。私もその方がいいと思う\n……莉央さんとうまくいくといいわね",
              "startTime": 448.0205010968,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.5733334208
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio001.wav",
      "text": "今日も残業に付き合ってくれて助かったわ\nおかげでプロジェクトも一段落ついたから\n今夜はパーッと飲みましょう",
      "startTime": 2.5000000875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh001.wav",
      "text": "はい！　ところで、今日の飲み会は\n俺と莉央さんだけなんですか？\nてっきり他にも人がいるのかと……",
      "startTime": 11.1000002146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.9000002146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio002.wav",
      "text": "前に約束したでしょ？\n貴方が仕事で一人前になったら\n私から飲みに誘ってあげるって",
      "startTime": 19.9000002146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio003.wav",
      "text": "{user}君のおかげで\nいつも助かってるわ。お礼に今夜は\n私がおごるから好きなものを注文しなさい",
      "startTime": 27.7000002146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.5666668813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh002.wav",
      "text": "そんな、悪いですよ\nお金なら俺も半分出しますから",
      "startTime": 35.5666668813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 40.4333312591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio004.wav",
      "text": "いいのよ\nたまには先輩らしいことをさせなさい",
      "startTime": 40.4333312591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh003.wav",
      "text": "たまにはだなんて……\n莉央さんは尊敬出来る\n素晴らしい先輩じゃないですか",
      "startTime": 44.4333312591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.5333312591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio005.wav",
      "text": "お世辞はいらないわ。裏ではみんな\n私のことを、怖いとか、厳しいとか\n口やかましいって言ってるんでしょ？",
      "startTime": 50.5333312591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh004.wav",
      "text": "莉央さんが厳しく叱るのは\n相手のためを思ってのことじゃないですか\nそれくらい莉央さんを見てれば分かります",
      "startTime": 58.6333284617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.566661795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio006.wav",
      "text": "貴方は私のことをちゃんと\n見てくれているのね\nありがとう。嬉しいわ",
      "startTime": 66.566661795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 72.9333284617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-rio007.wav",
      "text": "ふふ……今日は楽しいお酒が飲めそうね\nさあ、今夜は飲み明かすわよ",
      "startTime": 72.9333284617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 77.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "stop",
      "startTime": 80.183328271
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_stm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 80.866661795
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_03_01-koh005.wav",
      "text": "（素の莉央さんってこんな風に笑うんだ……\n会社では仕事人間のクールな姿しか\n見せないから、なんだか新鮮だな）",
      "startTime": 80.866661795,
      "sfxList": [
        {
